The zip icon packs bought from the website, usually contain size options available in 72x72 and 200x200.
- If you have a slow device, choose the 72x72 sized icons.
- For better devices, you can use 200x200 sized icons, but the size of the theme may be large, and will take longer to make than expected.
------------
Huge thanks to Ben Lee of http://www.bencodes.com for help with app-development.
This app does not require root. 
You must have 'allow unknown installations' enabled to install theme from sdcard

This app does require an internet connection to get the latest updates for the theme with each use. While the file is very small, we are not responsible for your data usage.
Permissions:
- USB Storage : Used to Build/Store theme on device
- Network communication : Only used to download latest source with each theme build.
